    public class FulfillRolesAction
extends org.eclipse.gef.ui.actions.SelectionAction
    This action is for adding to a Fulfillment the RoleTypes and the RoleGroups, which the source of the Fulfillment fulfills.
    Author:
    Kay Bierzynski

      • run

        public void run()
        In this method first the RolesDialog is prepared and started. After the user has closed the RolesDialog through the cancel button this method is finished as well. When the user has closed the RolesDialog through the ok button the choosen roles are added all at once to the Fulfillment through the FulfillRolesCommand.
        Specified by:
        run in interface org.eclipse.jface.action.IAction
        Overrides:
        run in class org.eclipse.jface.action.Action
